      <p>Nice.  Adding one lemon to my grocery list!  I have everything else!</p>
<p>A friend of mine taught me a great trick for dusting a cake with powdered sugar:  lay a lacy doily over top, sprinkle the sugar, carefully pull up the doily, and you&#39;ve got a pretty, lacy pattern.  You could also use those fridge magnet letters to spell something, or go wherever your imagination takes you!</p>
