      <p>I made this cake yesterday with a meyer lemon and an orange.  It came out perfectly (!) The almonds give the cake a little rough texture.  The marmaladey taste is perfect.  And it is even better the next day.  I&#39;ll have to wonder how it tastes on the 3rd day because it won&#39;t last that long.  Thanks so much for this recipe!</p>
    </div>

