    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=869#comment-18077"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-03-04T16:57:37-05:00">Thursday, March 4, 2010 at 4:57 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi:</p>
<p>Lovely cake &#8212; thanks very much for the recipe.</p>
<p>I used part of the batter for 12 <br />cupcakes in muffin pans lined with paper cupcake cups &#8212; baked about 30 minutes &#8212; check with a toothpick.</p>
<p>I baked the rest of the batter in 2 medium sized loaf pans sprayed with Pam &#8212; baked about 45 minutes &#8212; also check with a toothpick.</p>
<p>I frosted some of the cupcakes with a mix of powdered sugar, orange zest, &#038; orange juice &#8212; quite good, for those who insist on icing (men, in my experience).</p>
    </div>

