      <p>Just a note to those who don&#39;t have a food processor. Pureeing the orange and lemon works well with an immersion blender (a dinky one at that) and a little patience. I&#39;m sure it would do a fine job with the almonds, although my slightly obsessive-compulsive boyfriend went to town and achieved a near-powder texture with a knife alone.</p>
    </div>

