  <li id="comment-18118" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://keurigb155.livejournal.com/" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">keurigb155</a></cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=869#comment-18118"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-10-19T09:34:02-04:00">Tuesday, October 19, 2010 at 9:34 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My friend taught me a good trick for dusting a cake with powdered sugar: lay a lacy doily over top, sprinkle the sugar, carefully pull up the doily, and you&#39;ve got a pretty, lacy pattern.  </p>
<p>I used this many times and it really works great.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
