    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is the second time I&#39;ve made this cake, and it rocks <b>so</b> hard.  This time I really toasted the crap out of the almonds, and it&#39;s <b>so</b> worth it.</p>
<p>I don&#39;t have a blender, so I grind my almonds with a coffee grinder, and the citrus I combine with the olive oil and use my stick blender in a empty tin can.  beat my eggs with the stick blender too.  Who needs a KitchenAid?</p>
    </div>

